rge\nparameters, the impulse bit and the thrust-to-power ratio of the multi-anode\nVAT is able to be increased by a factor of 26 and 2.88 respectively compared\nwith the conventional VAT. Theoretical analysis and investigation of propulsion\nperformance validate the potential application advantages of the multi-anode\nVAT in the field of nanosatellite propulsion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2018 07:30:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2018 16:07:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2019 03:19:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-06"}
